1090
01:04:20,631 --> 01:04:22,504
Good, so you're
all set, right?

1091
01:04:22,548 --> 01:04:24,672
Yeah, I'm all set.

1092
01:04:25,798 --> 01:04:28,048
I don't like this
dress, I hate it,

1093
01:04:28,091 --> 01:04:29,632
