that the government
does and call it RICO,

1133
01:06:57,021 --> 01:07:03,102
it still stinks, it still
is rancid, it's still rotten,

1134
01:07:03,145 --> 01:07:06,729
it still makes you
retch and vomit.

1135
01:07:08,398 --> 01:07:10,521
But you can stop it!

1136
01:07:11,730 --> 01:07:16,730
