1173
01:09:55,870 --> 01:09:58,078
Look, I'm not even supposed
to be talkin' to you.

1174
01:09:58,121 --> 01:09:59,493
Hey, you're not doin' nothin'.

1175
01:09:59,537 --> 01:10:02,244
I'm the one doin'
all the talkin', huh?

1176
01:10:03,704 --> 01:10:08,745
Anyway, this is the
figure we had in mind.

1177
01:10:08,788 --> 01:10:11,621
