1178
01:10:11,664 --> 01:10:13,244
I don't know.

1179
01:10:13,287 --> 01:10:18,954
Hey, no pressure, you
don't have to decide now.

1180
01:10:18,997 --> 01:10:21,038
If you think we can do business,

1181
01:10:23,080 --> 01:10:26,164
just wear this handkerchief
