1219
01:12:28,260 --> 01:12:32,216
Now gentlemen, cool it!

1220
01:12:33,177 --> 01:12:38,134
(crowd murmuring)

1221
01:12:48,469 --> 01:12:50,509
Mmm, where's mine?

1222
01:12:50,552 --> 01:12:52,218
You didn't order anything.

1223
01:12:53,679 --> 01:12:55,927
