1252
01:15:36,901 --> 01:15:39,691
Genie and Joey, and
the other Johnny,

1253
01:15:39,734 --> 01:15:42,441
Willie Boy, and Arnold Pacara.

1254
01:15:42,485 --> 01:15:46,277
Indicating the main
defendants, among others.

